Happy Birthday, Syeda Manal Fatima 🌙

Born on 11 August 2005 — 11 August 2025
Syeda Manal Fatima, Ap meri zindagi ka wo ujala ho jo andheron ko bhi mohabbat ka rang data ha. 11-08-2005 ka din sirf Ap ka paida hone ka din nahi, balka mari duniya main ek nayi roshni ke janam ka din tha. Ap mari har subah ki muskaan, mari har shaam ka sakoon ho. Dua karta hoon ke Allah tumhe lambi umar, bepanah khushiyan aur wo sab da jo Ap na kabhi socha bhi na ho Ameen. Ap mari duaon ka wo hissa ho jo har saal nahi, har saans ke sath naya hota rehta hai.
